entries.s_10: I am A5 S5 tending droid for the Ice Cream Man, my current owner who has nick named me 'Ice Maker.'  No one refers to me as 'Otonon Tracks' any longer.
entries.s_12: Do you know anything about the construction of this fryer?  I am trying to reverse engineer it.
entries.s_14: The X34 model version 3.  I know that model as I revised a few parts for the version 4 schematic.  What would you like to know?
entries.s_16: Do you have any of the schematics by chance?
entries.s_20: Please wait.  I am scanning my memory banks.
entries.s_25: I cannot find any existing schematic data outside of the fryer diagram.  Do you want me to interface with your datapad and provide this information?
entries.s_27: Yes. Please uh, interface as you like.
entries.s_28: Done.  Now, may I take your order?
entries.s_31: I was hoping you could tell me where I could find out more regarding the fryer.
entries.s_32: You could just ask the Ice Cream Man for a copy of his schematic.
entries.s_34: Why didn't you tell me he had the schematic?  I could have just asked him.
entries.s_38: Hello.  I am A5 S5, a tending droid.  May I take your ice cream order?
entries.s_4: Hello. May I take your order?
entries.s_9: I am looking for a droid named 'Otonon Tracks.'  Are you, uh...him?
